queries.query:
from(bucket: "my-bucket")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "KELABO1-----BS1---KFU1")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "120210R01_FB_SEAT_Statistik_ZAU.120210R01.POR_OEE")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "my-bucket")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "KELABO1-----BS1---KFU1")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "120210R01_FB_SEAT_Statistik_ZAU.120210R01.POR_Disponibilidad")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
